Requires C11 compiler, like GCC >= 4.7.

* Recommended build:

=================================================
mkdir build
cd build
../configure
make
make check
[sudo] make install
=================================================

Thus, the headers files are goes to /usr/local/include/octothorpe and library file to /usr/local/lib.

* Debug build:

=================================================
mkdir build
cd build
../configure --enable-debug=yes
make
make check
[sudo] make install
=================================================

* MinGW:

How to set up both x86 and x64 MinGW compilers: http://yurichev.com/refs/mingw.html
